column5: Anyone else going up this weekend? Can't wait to get up there! We are staying at Keystone. I'm taking a buddy who has never fished up there before so I am hoping to show him a great time. Our 5th guy dropped out due to illness so if anyone knows sheepshead, we could use you!Anyone want to report on how the fishing has been? I hope to post a report when we come back.
Look forward to hearing back not only on the fishing but, on keystone as well. We will be there mid July and have high hopes that this will be our annual vacation destination
